===== Template screen =====

This class is designed to work with template screens. 

Object references: \\
  * [[manual:api:reference:templatescreen:object#template_screen|Template screen]]

Available methods: \\

  * ''[[manual:api:reference:templatescreen:copy|templatescreen.copy]]'' - copy template screens
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:templatescreen:create|templatescreen.create]]'' - create new template screens
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:templatescreen:delete|templatescreen.delete]]'' - delete template screens
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:templatescreen:get|templatescreen.get]]'' - retrieve template screens
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:templatescreen:update|templatescreen.update]]'' - update template screens